               <head>Rav pe῾alim by Joseph Zarka</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85100947" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>Grammatical writing.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="" class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85100947">
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="370v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Rav pe῾alim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">רב פעלים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Part one of the work, preceded by a preface and a table of contents, begins on folio 5r, part two on folio 28r, part three on folio 140r, and part four on folio 313v.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The author's colophon is given on folio 364v, followed by the date of 1483 as the date of copying.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Ta῾ame eme"t and ta῾ame ha-mikra are given on folios 366r-367r, but no additional table of contents follows. There are some notes on grammar on folio 1r. Lists of verbal forms, followed by the ten pesuḳim quoted by Rada"ḳ are given on folios 3v-4r.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/308277947">Zarka, Joseph</persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/308277947">זרקא, יוסף בן יהודה</persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
               </msContents>
               
               
               
