                  <additions>
                     
                     
                     
                     <p>Folio 368v: a statement in Latin on the age of the manuscript, written in 1639.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     <p>Folios 368-370 are fragments of a Latin service book with musical notation, written on parchment in black and red ink.</p>
                  
                  
                  
                  </additions>
                  
                  
                  
